{"tid":1417961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家記住 禮貌好重要","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:00.000Z","uid":122031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"87236d04e1e64bd41b69626bf1b1760be909c54b","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"我知道大家情緒可能比較燥 但係都請你保持冷靜深呼吸 唔好嚇親人先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢排去發夢當有人影相 啲兄弟就會好大反應而且係咁屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實佢唔係影緊大頭嘅咪俾佢影囉 反正自己都有必要戴口罩保護自己 但係如果講咗幾次佢都唔理嘅話你先大大力屌柒佢<br />\n因為有禮貌真係好重要!!!!<br />\n同埋要記住我哋嘅初衷 五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"2cd5de99c9f856cb75b81dbfbe444480e5dc0eb2","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f5e238c4fc42da35428a83a738a20b81e4ba5639","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:45:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"796b1a188050305b56b0a855ae2f21f9bcf617d4","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:45:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fac114d8acda772ecbbe25d4a8f5128108790a98","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d373f5a606a80ac66d090505909d0dc72d5ad9","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b266015ed914c944993ac30c13da1034fb46fc","tid":1417961,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0013b7118a8e06439f7314d5002bb1